## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7ebb0-1051">读取一个`XmlNode`从给定的读取器和将读取器定位到下一个节点。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebb0-1051">Reads one `XmlNode` from the given reader and positions the reader on the next node.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7ebb0-1052">此方法创建的一种`XmlNode`匹配<xref:System.Xml.XmlNode.NodeType%2A>当前定位读取器。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebb0-1052">This method creates the type of `XmlNode` matching the <xref:System.Xml.XmlNode.NodeType%2A> on which the reader is currently positioned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7ebb0-1053">(如果在读取器处于初始状态，`ReadNode`将读取器推进到第一个节点，然后在该节点上进行操作。)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebb0-1053">(If the reader is in the initial state, `ReadNode` advances the reader to the first node and then operates on that node.)</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7ebb0-1054">如果读取器定位在的开始处的元素，`ReadNode`读取所有属性和任何子节点，最多，并包括当前节点的结束标记。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebb0-1054">If the reader is positioned on the start of an element, `ReadNode` reads all the attributes and any child nodes, up to and including the end tag of the current node.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7ebb0-1055">`XmlNode`返回包含表示所读取所有内容的子树。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebb0-1055">The `XmlNode` returned contains the sub-tree representing everything read.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7ebb0-1056">读取器定位立即结束标记后面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebb0-1056">The reader is positioned immediately after the end tag.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7ebb0-1057">`ReadNode` 此外可以读取属性，但在这种情况下它不会不使读取器前进到下一个属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebb0-1057">`ReadNode` can also read attributes, but in this case it does not advance the reader to the next attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7ebb0-1058">此选项，可以编写以下 C# 代码：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebb0-1058">This allows you to write the following C# code:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XmlDocument doc = new XmlDocument();  
while (reader.MoveToNextAttribute())  
{  
  XmlNode a = doc.ReadNode(reader);  
  // Do some more processing.  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7ebb0-1059">`ReadNode` 未使用的属性值但是，这意味着在调用`ReadNode`特性，<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.ReadAttributeValue%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>返回`false`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ebb0-1059">`ReadNode` does consume the attribute value though, which means after calling `ReadNode` on an attribute, <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.ReadAttributeValue%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> returns `false`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
